<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-26 02:02 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2332 &Cx1f; tab-z
r a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SUDAN-`TOWEL-HEADS'-C     08-26 0972
