<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-26 11:20 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2787 &Cx1f; ttd-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CPT-DIGITALBAY-COLUMN     08-26 0892
