 (Repeating as part of a weekly roundup of computer features)  
SIDEBAR to DIGICAM 
By Kristi E. Swartz  
c. 1998 Cox News Service  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Still looking for more angles on digital cameras? The Internet
has sites devoted specifically to them. Online sites of computer
and tech magazines and sites from camera manufacturers can be an
additional guide, giving reviews and specific information about
each top buy.
</P>
