   HOCKEY GLOVES
</P>
<P>
   (FL) &UR; Men
</P>
<P>
   &LR; All-leather, longer
</P>
<P>
   &UR; Women &LR; (FR) &UR;
</P>
<P>
   &LR; 50-50 makeup of nylon of leather for more flexibiity; shorter.
</P>
