Obr &QL; 
Vietnamese &QL; 
Tagalog &QL; 
Arabic &QL; 
Nepali &QL; 
Assamese &QL; 
Prwa &QL; 
Thai &QL; 
Nigerian &QL; 
Albanian &QL; 
Iranian &QL;
</P>
