<P>
   TITANIC-VIDEO (Los Angeles) _ The home video version of
``Titanic'' will hit stores one minute past midnight Monday with
Paramount already shipping more than 20 million copies. Blockbuster
will open the doors at many outlets at midnight to appease DiCaprio
fans. ``Titanic'' will cross over the $600 million mark in domestic
theatrical grosses this weekend. By Dave McNary.
</P>
