review of a glucose sensor from MiniMed Inc. that could result in
its approval before the year is out. The sensor is placed under a
diabetic's skin to monitor their blood sugar level and would be
pared with MiniMed's insulin pump to keep those levels safe. By Ben
Sullivan.
