<HEADLINE>
EXPERTS QUESTION MILITARY STRIKES IN TARGETING BIN LADEN 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (EDs: Refiling to eliminate garble)   (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By NICOLE TSONG  
 c.1998 Hearst Newspapers  
<TEXT>
