<P>
   FUNDRAISING-GORE (Washington) _ Attorney General Janet Reno
advances a step closer to asking for an independent prosecutor to
investigate Vice President Al Gore's role in fund raising for the
1996 campaign by ordering a 90-day preliminary inquiry into whether
Gore lied to investigators last year when he was initially
interviewed about his telephone solicitations from the White House.
By David Johnston. (We plan to move the story by 9 p.m. ET in ``w''
news file.)
</P>
