Tropical-storm-force wind and rain lashed the Atlantic coast as the
Hurricane Bonnie reached the mainland Wednesday afternoon. By Kevin
Sack. (Scheduled to move by 9 p.m. ET in ``a'' news file.) Story
runs under 3-column photo.
