   NYMAYOR-FUNDRAISING _ Mayor Rudolph Giuliani is raising money
for other Republicans in Wisconsin and Iowa, where the question
centers on his political plans. Many Iowans seem impressed when he
notes that the number of murders in New York City has declined
during his tenure to 800 a year from 2,000. Many also say they are
familiar with the mayor through his appearances on David Letterman
and the Tonight Show. By Dan Barry. (Scheduled to move by 9 p.m. ET
in ``a'' news file.)
